Public Methods

public CarVendorExtensionManager getManager (String serviceName)

Returns a CarVendorExtensionManager based on the vendor extension channel in the GAL protocol.

Parameters
serviceName String: The name of the configured service to return.
Returns
CarVendorExtensionManager The manager if it is available, null if the extension is not found. A SecurityException will be thrown if the caller does not have permissions to access the channel.
Throws
CarNotConnectedException if the car has become disconnected.
SecurityException
